    "body": "GpuTransitionOverride.getOptimizedSortOrder currently assumes that as long as an expression is supported, the SortOrder of that expression is also supported.  This is not true for all cases, as libcudf does not support sorting lists of structs or structs of lists.  In practice this means a user setting spark.rapids.sql.hashOptimizeSort.enabled=true could have query crash because the RAPIDS Accelerator tries to sort on an unsupported ordering type.",
